contentrichtext.text: {{Infobox French commune |name = Quistinic |native name = Kistinid |image=France - Morbihan - Quistinic - Poul Fétan.jpg |longitude=-3.1331 |latitude=47.9058 |INSEE = 56188 |postal code = 56310 |department = [[Morbihan]] |arrondissement = Lorient |canton = Plouay |mayor = Gisèle Guilbart |term = 2008—2014 |intercommunality = Région de Plouay |elevation min m = 20 |elevation max m = 177 |area km2 = 42.95 |population = 1312 |population date = 1999 }} '''Quistinic''' ({{Lang-br|Kistinid}}) is a [[Communes of France|commune]] in the [[Morbihan]] [[Departments of France|department]] of [[Brittany (administrative region)|Brittany]] in north-western [[France]]. ==Demographics== Inhabitants of Quistinic are called in [[French language|French]] ''Quistinicois''. ==See also== *[[Communes of the Morbihan department]] ==References== * [http://www.maires56.asso.fr Mayors of Morbihan Association] {{Fr icon}} * [http://www.insee.fr/fr/methodes/nomenclatures/cog/fichecommunale.asp?codedep=56&codecom=188 INSEE commune file] ==External links== * [http://patrimoine.region-bretagne.fr/main.xsp?execute=show_document&id=MERIMEEIA56005651 Cultural Heritage] {{Fr icon}} {{Morbihan communes}} [[Category:Communes of Morbihan]] {{Morbihan-geo-stub}}
